---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import barsImg from "../assets/images/bars.jpg";
---

<section id="about" class="bg-background py-12 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      <div class="text-left">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-text">About Volcanic Spirits</h2>
        <p class="font-body mt-6 text-lg text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
          We are a team with over a decade of experience in international trade and a deep love for Mexican spirits. Our
          mission is to bring authentic brands of tequila, mezcal, raicilla, sotol, and other agave treasures to the
          heart of the United States, opening paths for their essence to conquer new palates.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body mt-4 text-lg text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
          At Volcanic Spirits, we believe that every drop of Mexican spirit is a living story: the strength of volcanic
          soil, the patience of agave, the artistry of expert hands, and the heritage of generations.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="group inline-flex items-center mt-8 font-bold text-text hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          Learn More
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1"
          >
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <Image
          src={barsImg}
          alt="Un jimador trabajando en un campo de agave"
          quality="mid"
          class="w-full max-w-md object-cover rounded-lg shadow-xl shadow-secondary/10"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
